originalText.text: I've had a fantastic experience with Extra Space Storage. Juan was terrific. The facility is clean, well-maintained, and the staff is incredibly helpful. The security measures in place give me peace of mind, and the convenience of access hours makes it easy to retrieve my belongings. I highly recommend Extra Space Storage for anyone in need of reliable and secure storage solutions.

originalText.text: Coming in this morning I didn’t know what to expect. I met one of the most amazing, talented, helpful associate from your company. They were very knowledgeable about your product and seem to know exactly what I would need to accommodate my current exigencies. In addition, they were very warm, helpful and courteous to me. They really made me feel like I mattered to your company and that alone had sold me on taking three bins instead of two. I truly appreciate the way I was taken care of! I pray that this note finds every member of your staff  in good health.

originalText.text: Since 2017 Im a loyal Extra Space customer at 58 W 143rd St Ny, Ny 10037. Everyone in the facility are truly amazing and very nice. They helped me in everything I need in the facility especially if I need to transfer in the Unit I need either bigger or smaller unit I never encountered any problem about it. Until this JACKIE referred herself as the facility “Manager” I reserved a Unit that quite bigger than I currently have l, since I saw online rate are quite discounted. I asked her if she could help me to get the unit I need and ofcourse I politely asked her if I can possibly get those discounted unit, atleast I can save a little extra. Since our current unit is full and our stuff is not fit at all I told her she can take a look at. She told me that “you’re account could be redflag for doing a price hopping” she told me in a blunt tone. I asked her politely if I can possibly get a online rate if NOT, she can explain it politely in a professional way. Then I asked her to show me the Unit id like to see if my stuff will fit in there but she told me“i showed it to you already” I told her the one she showed me is different from the one I newly reserved. Shes hesitant and looked irritated to showed me the unit in the basement which 1 unit has leaked then she told me she will not giving me the Online rate discount and I could get redflag for the price hopping. This Jackie “the manager” can simply explain it to me that I am not eligible for discount but instead she said it  in accusation way for price hopping. is it because im Asian she will treat me that way? Like I said im a loyal Extra Space since 2017 and no one in the facility treated me the way she treated me. As a loyal customer I just only asked if Im eligible to get the Online price since I needed bigger unit for my stuff because my current unit was totally full if NOT and Im NOT eligible she can just explain it to me in a professional way.

originalText.text: One of the most refreshing storage space experiences I've had so far! I want to mention Jacqueline specifically, she was kind and professional. She knew how to articulate and explain the various pricing and sizing of each unit very well, and made it easy to find a unit that works for me!
